cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum value 'bad' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為無效的枚舉值 'bad' 會導致配置解析失敗，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
